tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE ProteinInteractionNetwork (
  protein_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  interaction_partner_id INT,
  interaction_type VARCHAR(50),
  interaction_strength DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE ProteinInteractions (
  interaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  protein1 VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  protein2 VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  interaction_type VARCHAR(50),
  interaction_score FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE protein_interactions (
    interaction_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    protein1_id UUID,
    protein2_id UUID,
    interaction_type VARCHAR(50),
    interaction_score FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE interaction_analysis (
    analysis_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    protein_id INT,
    partner_id INT,
    type_id INT,
    analysis_date TIMESTAMP
);
CREATE TABLE ProteinInteractionNetwork (id INT PRIMARY KEY, protein1_name VARCHAR(255), protein2_name VARCHAR(255), interaction_type VARCHAR(50));
CREATE TABLE ProteinLocalization (id INT PRIMARY KEY, protein_name VARCHAR(255), localization VARCHAR(50));
CREATE TABLE ProteinStructure (id INT PRIMARY KEY, protein_name VARCHAR(255), structure_file VARCHAR(255));
CREATE TABLE InteractionEvidence (id INT PRIMARY KEY, interaction_id INT, evidence_text TEXT);
CREATE TABLE ExperimentalMethods (id INT PRIMARY KEY, method_name VARCHAR(100), description TEXT);
